CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Stryve Foods Inc is focused on manufacturing and marketing highly differentiated healthy snacks that disrupt traditional snacking categories. It offers convenient snacks that are lower in sugar and carbohydrates and higher in protein than other snacks. Stryve offers all-natural, delicious snacks which it believes are a nutritious and conveniently healthy snacking option for on-the-go lives.
